msgctxt "sn40.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 40 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 40 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Moggallānavagga "
msgstr "1. By Moggallāna "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn40.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Ākiñcaññāyatanapañhāsutta "
msgstr "7. A Question About the Dimension of Nothingness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn40.7:1.1"
msgid "“‘Ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ, ākiñcaññāyatanan’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“They speak of this thing called the ‘dimension of nothingness’. "

msgctxt "sn40.7:1.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho ākiñcaññāyatananti? "
msgstr "What is the dimension of nothingness? "

msgctxt "sn40.7:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi: "
msgstr "It occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn40.7:1.4"
msgid "‘idha bhikkhu sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma natthi kiñcīti ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "‘It’s when a mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of infinite consciousness, aware that “there is nothing at all”, enters and remains in the dimension of nothingness. "

msgctxt "sn40.7:1.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati ākiñcaññāyatanan’ti. "
msgstr "This is called the dimension of nothingness.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.7:1.6"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma natthi kiñcīti ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
msgstr "And so … I was entering and remaining in the dimension of nothingness. "

msgctxt "sn40.7:1.7"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, iminā vihārena viharato viññāṇañcāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. "
msgstr "While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by the dimension of infinite consciousness beset me. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.268, sc2
msgctxt "sn40.7:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, āvuso, bhagavā iddhiyā upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha came up to me with his psychic power and said, "

msgctxt "sn40.7:2.2"
msgid "‘moggallāna, moggallāna. "
msgstr "‘Moggallāna, Moggallāna! "

msgctxt "sn40.7:2.3"
msgid "Mā, brāhmaṇa, ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ pamādo, ākiñcaññāyatane cittaṃ saṇṭhapehi, ākiñcaññāyatane cittaṃ ekodiṃ karohi, ākiñcaññāyatane cittaṃ samādahā’ti. "
msgstr "Don’t neglect the dimension of nothingness, brahmin! Settle your mind in the dimension of nothingness; unify your mind and immerse it in the dimension of nothingness.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.7:2.4"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, aparena samayena sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma natthi kiñcīti ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. "
msgstr "And so, after some time … I entered and remained in the dimension of nothingness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.7:2.5"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, āvuso, sammā vadamāno vadeyya … pe … mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti. "
msgstr "So if anyone should be rightly called a disciple who attained to great direct knowledge with help from the Teacher, it’s me.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn40.7:2.6"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

